  <img imageRotate="0" src="assets/pastedtext.png" /> 
  <h3 id="#SpecialCharacters">Insert special characters in text</h3> 
  <p>The Agent UI has built in support for 210 special characters. The admin can <a href="../../forms/using/custom-special-characters.md">add support for more/custom special characters by customization</a>. </p> 
