  <h4 id="AttachmentDelivery">Attachment delivery</h4> 
  <ul> 
   <li>When the Interactive Communication is rendered using Server-side APIs as an interactive or non-interactive PDF, the rendered PDF contains attachments as PDF attachments.</li> 
   <li>When a post process associated with an Interactive Communication is loaded as part of the Submit using Agent UI, attachments are passed as the List&amp;lt;com.adobe.idp.Document&amp;gt; inAttachmentDocs parameter.</li> 
   <li>Delivery mechanism workflows, such as email and print, also deliver attachments along with the PDF version of the Interactive Communication.</li> 
  </ul> 
