  <ul> 
   <li><strong>Up/Down arrows</strong>: Arrows to move document fragments up or down in the Interactive Communication.</li> 
   <li><strong>Delete</strong>: If allowed, delete the document fragment from the Interactive Communication. </li> 
   <li><strong>Page Break Before</strong> (applicable for child fragments of target area): Inserts page break before the document fragment.</li> 
